        "Description": "Good Evening Agent 47\rYour target this time is a terrorist group known simply as The Silence\rIntel has shown that Silence operatives Bernie Valladares and Jose Alvarez are meeting with military contractors Joseph Renda and Leopoldo Olmeda\rIf The Silence manages to connect with these operatives they will obtain the ability to hack into the United States missile systems and start a nuclear war with the only outcome being total global annihilation \rStop them before that happens \rGood luck 47",
